# Why next_start?

Consider

```
1 3 5 4 2 6 8
```

Current bitonic

```
1 3 5 4 2
```

When we reach

```
4
```

We already know

```
2
```

cannot belong to next increasing sequence.

So next subarray should begin from

```
2
```

Hence

```
next_start = j + 1
```

when descent starts.

